All 5 tests pass. The fix is one line: calling `ApplyIconStyle(IconStyle)` in the `IconButton` constructor ensures the `collapseToggle` class and `ChevronIcon` child are applied even when `IconStyle` stays at its default enum value (0), which otherwise wouldn't trigger the `Changed` handler in Avalonia.

